# .gitignore Rules for ts-git-garden

## Required Patterns:

```gitignore
# Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp
.pnp.js

# Production builds
/dist
/build
*.tsbuildinfo

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# Testing
/coverage
*.lcov

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
.vscode/extensions.json
.vscode/settings.json
.idea
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Cursor rules
!.cursor/rules/
!.cursor/rules/*.mdc

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Vite
.vite
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo
.tscache/

# Optional npm cache directory
.npm

# Optional eslint cache
.eslintcache

# Output of 'npm pack'
*.tgz

# Yarn
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz
.pnp.*

# Build artifacts
/dist-ssr
*.local

# Cache directories
.cache/
.parcel-cache/

# Temporary files
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
*.temp

# Container artifacts (if building containers)
*.tar
*.tar.gz
```

## Must NOT Ignore:

```gitignore
# Keep these committed
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
!.github/
!.cursor/rules/
!.cursor/rules/*.mdc
```

## Project-Specific Additions:

If ts-git-garden has specific build outputs or generated files, add them but document why.